title: Quick Mumbai-Spiced Chicken & Carrot Noodle Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Coriander
description: It’s good to relax and refresh, and a good meal can be the first step! Our Mumbai spice blend adds mild and
fragrant flavours to delicate chicken breast. Served on a bed of carrot noodles and tossed in a salad, this meal is sure to
rejuvenate you at the end of a long day.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
